((F_F)>> filter :@
    :F p (/>_<)/~o :F l (/>_<)/~o 
        (?_?) __ B= l []
        (T_T) []
        (E_E) (?_?) __ p _ head l 
              (T_T) __ >V< 
                    _ head l 
                    __ filter p _ tail l
              (E_E) __ filter p _ tail l

((F_F)>> isEven :@
    :F x (/>_<)/~o __ B= __ :% x 2 0

__ filter isEven __ >V< 1 >V< 2 >V< 3 >V< 4 >V< 5 >V< 6 []